title: The 13th Warrior (Antonio Banderos, Omar Sharif)
description: Antonio Banderos stars in this gripping tale of an exhiled embassador (Banderos) comes across a band of fierce warriors he is told by an old fortune-teller that he is the 13th warrior to join the the hunt in a far off land to kill the ferocious creatures that are devouring all living things in their path.  Omar Sharif urges him to take a chance, will Ahmed overcome his fears and understand his fellow warriors in time to face the horror that awaits them or will the beasts of legend murder them all first.
